{"id":584642,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/亲友会-母亲节下午我目睹了一场彩虹风暴和暴力/","date":"2018-05-14T06:58:51Z","modified":"2018-05-14T06:58:51Z","title":"亲友会 | 母亲节下午我目睹了一场彩虹风暴和暴力执法","content":"<p>同性恋亲友会北京分会今天母亲节活动有三个环节：和同志妈妈们中午聚餐；游览798艺术区；4点钟到798创意广场支持“我的票圈”发起的发放彩虹勋章的活动。</p>\n<p>当我们游览完798，4点钟准时赶到创意广场时，发现人数寥寥，和一个女孩交流后，她说大家都去了北门。</p>\n<p>于是我们一行人——有同志妈妈，有少数民族穆斯林同志，有加班翘班过来的同志，有同志情侣，有刚刚加入的亲友会的志愿者……，前往北门。刚出北门就被震惊了，马路上都是人，有几百人在排队，等着和票圈君拥抱，领取彩虹胸章，大家安安静静，秩序井然，也没有相互聊天，都在安静地低头看自己的手机。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/11441095-9725-4506-a501-62046810ac1c.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584645\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/11441095-9725-4506-a501-62046810ac1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/11441095-9725-4506-a501-62046810ac1c.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/11441095-9725-4506-a501-62046810ac1c-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/11441095-9725-4506-a501-62046810ac1c-768x433.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/11441095-9725-4506-a501-62046810ac1c-1024x577.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这就是身穿“无法查看，404”T恤的年轻帅气的票圈君。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e272adab-dd55-4d0d-873f-f5f1712209cf.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584646\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e272adab-dd55-4d0d-873f-f5f1712209cf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e272adab-dd55-4d0d-873f-f5f1712209cf.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e272adab-dd55-4d0d-873f-f5f1712209cf-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e272adab-dd55-4d0d-873f-f5f1712209cf-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e272adab-dd55-4d0d-873f-f5f1712209cf-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>小伙伴们依次拥抱票圈君，下面是部分拥抱的瞬间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0a6814f1-dc0e-46f2-b94e-5ef88c268339.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584647\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0a6814f1-dc0e-46f2-b94e-5ef88c268339.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0a6814f1-dc0e-46f2-b94e-5ef88c268339.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0a6814f1-dc0e-46f2-b94e-5ef88c268339-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0a6814f1-dc0e-46f2-b94e-5ef88c268339-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0a6814f1-dc0e-46f2-b94e-5ef88c268339-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1dc5e402-6a5b-4c5e-90db-43937a7b723f.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584648\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1dc5e402-6a5b-4c5e-90db-43937a7b723f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1dc5e402-6a5b-4c5e-90db-43937a7b723f.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1dc5e402-6a5b-4c5e-90db-43937a7b723f-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1dc5e402-6a5b-4c5e-90db-43937a7b723f-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1dc5e402-6a5b-4c5e-90db-43937a7b723f-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b5fdb8dd-1009-4b77-bd77-e868f9329fa4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584649\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b5fdb8dd-1009-4b77-bd77-e868f9329fa4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b5fdb8dd-1009-4b77-bd77-e868f9329fa4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b5fdb8dd-1009-4b77-bd77-e868f9329fa4-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b5fdb8dd-1009-4b77-bd77-e868f9329fa4-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b5fdb8dd-1009-4b77-bd77-e868f9329fa4-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/f5163bcf-48a9-449f-9eff-dc758fbeff31.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584651\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/f5163bcf-48a9-449f-9eff-dc758fbeff31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/f5163bcf-48a9-449f-9eff-dc758fbeff31.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/f5163bcf-48a9-449f-9eff-dc758fbeff31-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/f5163bcf-48a9-449f-9eff-dc758fbeff31-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/f5163bcf-48a9-449f-9eff-dc758fbeff31-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c62f5b77-7cb5-4408-a6d2-7d37774fc349.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584650\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c62f5b77-7cb5-4408-a6d2-7d37774fc349.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c62f5b77-7cb5-4408-a6d2-7d37774fc349.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c62f5b77-7cb5-4408-a6d2-7d37774fc349-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c62f5b77-7cb5-4408-a6d2-7d37774fc349-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c62f5b77-7cb5-4408-a6d2-7d37774fc349-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>同性恋亲友会北京分会的志愿者潘妈妈是专程来支持这个活动的，72岁的老人排着队等待拥抱。她说：“孩子们你们要勇敢做自己，现在的社会风气多好啊”。潘阿姨和票圈君拥抱。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/18f85d93-6f78-43f7-97ab-2829b389c61a.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584652\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/18f85d93-6f78-43f7-97ab-2829b389c61a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/18f85d93-6f78-43f7-97ab-2829b389c61a.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/18f85d93-6f78-43f7-97ab-2829b389c61a-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/18f85d93-6f78-43f7-97ab-2829b389c61a-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/18f85d93-6f78-43f7-97ab-2829b389c61a-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>王嘉宇、潘妈妈和票圈君合影。潘妈妈手里拿的是志愿者送给她的母亲节鲜花。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/9f90def0-c099-454a-bd15-e94c37cc044c.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584653\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/9f90def0-c099-454a-bd15-e94c37cc044c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/9f90def0-c099-454a-bd15-e94c37cc044c.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/9f90def0-c099-454a-bd15-e94c37cc044c-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/9f90def0-c099-454a-bd15-e94c37cc044c-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/9f90def0-c099-454a-bd15-e94c37cc044c-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>很多人是远道而来专程支持，也有很多是刚刚听到有这样的活动，决定支持彩虹拥抱活动的。因为队伍越来越长，已经把798创意广场的路口堵住了，票圈君不得不一再往东后撤。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c124d82b-959c-4066-ad04-cd95f9d8078b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584654\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c124d82b-959c-4066-ad04-cd95f9d8078b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c124d82b-959c-4066-ad04-cd95f9d8078b.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c124d82b-959c-4066-ad04-cd95f9d8078b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c124d82b-959c-4066-ad04-cd95f9d8078b-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/c124d82b-959c-4066-ad04-cd95f9d8078b-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>从始至终，大家都是秩序井然，而且一直有志愿者在维持秩序。</p>\n<p>但因为这场活动是票圈君在“我的票圈”公众号和微博上发起的，所以很多慕名前来支持的同时，也惊动了警察。在798创意广场，今天特意在广场南北停着两辆警车，多位警察在现场，严阵以待，平时广场上很空旷，今天不仅有警车和警察，广场上也忽然多了很多车辆停泊。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584655\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b-300x182.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b-768x466.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b-1024x622.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/34a0905b-b792-4b77-b575-80bff5e0233b-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>因为现场人越来越多，不断有人加入，有人建议立即停止活动，说“已经聚集了近千人”。所以大家决定停止拥抱活动，把彩虹胸章发放给大家。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e2f76df0-5a2d-448e-a402-087eb8401434.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584656\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e2f76df0-5a2d-448e-a402-087eb8401434.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"615\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e2f76df0-5a2d-448e-a402-087eb8401434.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e2f76df0-5a2d-448e-a402-087eb8401434-219x300.jpg 219w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e2f76df0-5a2d-448e-a402-087eb8401434-768x1050.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/e2f76df0-5a2d-448e-a402-087eb8401434-749x1024.jpg 749w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后人群逐渐散去。</p>\n<p>没有想到有如此多的人前来支持，领取并佩戴彩虹胸章。我们亲眼目睹了一场青春风暴，看到了希望和力量，但活动和参与者并不仅仅是年轻人，还有孩子、老人，还有附近居民。大家感受着活动带来的群情振奋，以及彼此带给对方的温暖和热情。活动本身非常和谐，令人感动。</p>\n<p>但在798入口处，突发意外。几名798艺术去区门口的特勤警察（负责城市反恐和维稳，隶属于公安局系统），突然对一个穿蓝色背带短裤和一个短发女孩拳打脚踢，微胖的短裤女孩被保安重拳殴打，用蛮力强行拉到，短发女孩被连续重拳打在胸部和腹部。等我掏出手机，殴打已经结束，两人蹲在地上，暂时站不起来。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ee644a40-4afa-40ae-8131-3aabe12fe6aa.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584660\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ee644a40-4afa-40ae-8131-3aabe12fe6aa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ee644a40-4afa-40ae-8131-3aabe12fe6aa.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ee644a40-4afa-40ae-8131-3aabe12fe6aa-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ee644a40-4afa-40ae-8131-3aabe12fe6aa-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/ee644a40-4afa-40ae-8131-3aabe12fe6aa-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b1c0d0b5-53dd-42c4-8b11-c5ee16469841.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584659\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b1c0d0b5-53dd-42c4-8b11-c5ee16469841.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b1c0d0b5-53dd-42c4-8b11-c5ee16469841.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b1c0d0b5-53dd-42c4-8b11-c5ee16469841-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b1c0d0b5-53dd-42c4-8b11-c5ee16469841-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/b1c0d0b5-53dd-42c4-8b11-c5ee16469841-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/08f9d945-202d-4a33-9d37-6d5e01bcb563.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584657\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/08f9d945-202d-4a33-9d37-6d5e01bcb563.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/08f9d945-202d-4a33-9d37-6d5e01bcb563.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/08f9d945-202d-4a33-9d37-6d5e01bcb563-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/08f9d945-202d-4a33-9d37-6d5e01bcb563-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/08f9d945-202d-4a33-9d37-6d5e01bcb563-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/a667f65e-3856-4fb4-9ed1-d0e3972cb66f.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584658\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/a667f65e-3856-4fb4-9ed1-d0e3972cb66f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/a667f65e-3856-4fb4-9ed1-d0e3972cb66f.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/a667f65e-3856-4fb4-9ed1-d0e3972cb66f-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/a667f65e-3856-4fb4-9ed1-d0e3972cb66f-768x433.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/a667f65e-3856-4fb4-9ed1-d0e3972cb66f-1024x577.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这个短发女孩的嘴角被拳头扫到，肘部有擦伤。另外的穿蓝背带裤的女孩已经不见了。旁观者拨打了110，特勤打人，110能否秉公执法，不袒护自己人？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3acefc65-9803-4cb4-9323-839f4fc843e2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584661\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3acefc65-9803-4cb4-9323-839f4fc843e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3acefc65-9803-4cb4-9323-839f4fc843e2.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3acefc65-9803-4cb4-9323-839f4fc843e2-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3acefc65-9803-4cb4-9323-839f4fc843e2-768x1360.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3acefc65-9803-4cb4-9323-839f4fc843e2-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这就是几位暴力执法的、穿着“特勤”服装的人。</p>\n<p>798艺术区向来以开放、包容著称，所以活动选择在了798艺术区，但遵守秩序参加活动的人，却遭遇了野蛮暴力执法，非常非常令人感到遗憾。</p>\n<p>两个女孩被打视频和现场活动视频稍后上传到腾讯视频，敬请关注。</p>\n<p>尽管网络视听协会把同性恋和乱伦、变态并置；尽管天涯社区删除了曾陪伴同志十多年的“一路同行”专区；尽管新浪曾要删除所有同性恋相关的视频和动画内容；尽管现在仍然有很多的教材仍然视同性恋为变态，但都不能阻止LBGT想要生活在阳光下、想要做真实的自己的决心。而且就像今天这场人数庞大的现场活动一样，越来越多人对同志群体表示理解和支持。愿所有的人都能在阳光下自由表达、活出真我。愿中国在崛起、复兴和强国的道路上，能够日益开放、包容、多元。</p>\n<p>为所有到现场对LGBT群体进行支持的人表示衷心感谢！祝所有母亲节日快乐！</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[34613,27316,34340,34612,34615,34614,10367,34396,9503]}